  "text": "For image deblurring problems, we use 0.2 × Tol instead of Tol for [CITATION_1] in order to prevent our algorithm from stopping prematurely. The scaling constant 0.2 was found after some experimentation. We also stop the APG algorithm when the relative error of the iterates satisfies the following condition:",
